data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the Ridges at Loudoun Valley! This beautiful 3-level townhouse condo offers a perfect blend of elegance, comfort, and convenience.  Step inside to discover a stunning main level adorned with gleaming wood floors that lead you up to an inviting, open floor plan and fresh new paint throughout. The heart of the home is the gourmet kitchen, boasting stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, ample cabinet space, a white subway tile backsplash, an island, and a charming breakfast nook. Whether you're entertaining guests or preparing a cozy meal, this kitchen is sure to impress.  Relax and unwind in the spacious living room, ideal for cozy evenings or gatherings with loved ones. Adjacent to the kitchen is a versatile office space, perfect for remote work or study sessions. Step outside to the covered balcony overlooking the community's green space.  Upstairs, you'll find a luxurious primary bedroom complete with a walk-in closet and an en suite bathroom, offering a private retreat at the end of the day. An additional bedroom with and bathroom provides ample space for guests or family members.  This home is not just about luxury; it's also about convenience and low-maintenance living. With LPV flooring (upper level), a washer and dryer on the upper level as well, and a fire sprinkler system, every detail has been meticulously crafted for your comfort and peace of mind.  Beyond the walls of your new home lies a vibrant community filled with first-class amenities. Enjoy access to three pools, two fitness centers, tennis courts, walking trails, and tot lots, ensuring there's always something to do for every member of the family. Another bonus is low HOA and condo fees.  Nestled in a prime location, you're just moments away from Brambleton's finest restaurants, shopping destinations, and entertainment options. Plus, the Silver Line Metro station, Dulles Airport, and major parks await just around the corner.  Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity to call the Ridges at Loudoun Valley home. Visit our open house on Feb.17, 12-2 pm, Sun Feb. 18, 12-2 pm.
